title: Sort by popularity
body:
Make the photos or feedback sortable by most "liked"
Can also make photos sortable by other features (e.g. time taken, alphabetical username).

title: Map of Locations
body: Create a page that maps the location of the last 50 photos using the longitude/latitude.
